{"tid":697253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德國再傳難民性侵女性 14歲女孩遭棄屍荒野","createTime":"2018-06-10T23:41:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T10:58:54.000Z","uid":141151,"like":254,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"0d5039cfedc329512f7395744d2fb02b8637a350","tid":697253,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T23:41:19.000Z","msg":"德國再傳難民性侵女性 14歲女孩遭棄屍荒野<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2452962\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2452962&d=l9VKxDsGp6iGW%2FHX6EPx8CwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=19f74801\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2452962&h=0a5b10c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2452962</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕德國頻傳難民姦淫、殺害女性的案件，2016年，歐盟高官19歲女兒拉登伯格（Maria Ladenburger）在佛萊堡遇害，行兇的阿富汗難民一審被判終身監禁；同年還有2名在波鴻求學的中國女留學生遭到性侵，犯案的伊拉克難民被判11年有期徒刑，如今又傳出14歲女孩被難民姦殺棄屍的案件。<br />\n<br />\n據《德國之聲》報導，14歲少女蘇珊娜（Susanna）失蹤兩週後，遺體在德國中部城市威斯巴登的埃爾本海姆（Wiesbaden-Erbenheim）一處荒地被發現，經過屍檢後證實生前遭到性侵與暴力。<br />\n<br />\n德國警方原先鎖定2名重大嫌疑人，並逮捕其中1名35歲的土耳其難民，但後來因罪證不足釋放，至於另1位更有嫌疑的20歲伊拉克難民阿里（Ali B.），竟然在犯案後的6月初大搖大擺地和家人搭機出境回到伊拉克。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">警方表示，阿里是在2015年秋天來到德國避難，之後經常在警局留下案底，不久前還被指控性侵11歲的女童，但證據不足終止了調查。阿里此次出境利用他人姓名購買機票，而機場海關沒有檢查他的機票和德國居留證姓名是否一致。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n雖然法網恢恢，阿里在8日傳出在伊拉克遭到逮捕，不過德國多個政黨領導人對此案莫不義憤填膺，右派的自由民主黨黨主席林德納（Christian Linder）怒批，兇手竟然可以使用假名出境；極右派的另類選擇黨黨主席威德爾（Alice Weidel），則痛斥德國總理梅克爾接納難民的政策。<br />\n<br />\n但<span style=\"color: red;\">也有不少聲音呼籲民眾冷靜，別將犯罪個案與難民群體混為一談，也要避免右翼民粹主義者渲染此案以達到政治目的。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f948a446821748e4aeac261e845ad0abd9b05b5","tid":697253,"uid":108090,"like":233,"dislike":1,"score":232,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T23:44:47.000Z","msg":"啱架啦 引入多啲難民啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n班難民又冇名聲又冇錢<br />\n犯罪嘅代價極低<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf6dd8b1201f1e8557d254e44ad74d22f01ef06","tid":697253,"uid":49392,"like":21,"dislike":7,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T23:46:31.000Z","msg":"Ali原來係咁嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b79e52175bc4969bceb87b43a9cca6e9109936f","tid":697253,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T00:30:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33f00d761e668769a441c4a47925f374e93a6008","tid":697253,"uid":52946,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T00:31:18.000Z","msg":"犯罪咁少 等班難民幫你地沖下數"},{"pid":"2def7cb3e46d109d0d5cc7ffb9c51e12703203ef","tid":697253,"uid":2054,"like":86,"dislike":0,"score":86,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T00:33:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">welcome refugees</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b7cabc3de72c4b2acabde2cbd1e71a1d479ca69","tid":697253,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2def7cb3e46d109d0d5cc7ffb9c51e12703203ef","tid":697253,"uid":2054,"like":86,"dislike":0,"score":86,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T00:33:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">welcome refugees</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T00:34:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b37cd6